ntral to their work. More specifically, they had to find a suitable stand-in for, you guessed it, the humble, powerful, usually ubiquitous whiteboard.The sudden need to replicate brainstorming online has increased the popularity of collaborative, digital whiteboards. But it\xe2\x80\x99s also led to other creative in-house solutions.Image copyright: MuralA MURAL brainstorm in action.\xe2\x80\x9cWe found both the value of some of the new tools has surprised us, [as well as] our workarounds to creating great experiences with clients\xe2\x80\xa6it has created its own interesting kind of energy,\xe2\x80\x9d says Clark Scheffy, a partner and managing director at IDEO, a global design consultancy. \xe2\x80\x9cI believe when we return to whatever this next world is after the pandemic, many\xc2\xa0of the things we\xe2\x80\x99ve discovered and created will continue because they provide a unique value.\xe2\x80\x9dConsultants keep many industries moving smoothly along, but how to consult during Covid? Read this week\xe2\x80\x99s field guide to take a lesson from how the consulting world is coping.Becoming a member directly supports the work we do and gives you access to every bit of it. For a limited time, become a Quartz member for 20% off. Use promo code QZTWENTY at checkout.\xe2\x9c\xa8 Become a Quartz member \xe2\x9c\xa8Power to the young peopleImage copyright: Reuters/Temilade AdelajaJust one message.\xe2\x80\x9cThese protests are different because they are decentralized and not directed by \xe2\x80\x9cleaders\xe2\x80\x9d or typical \xe2\x80\x9cactivists.\xe2\x80\x9dOver the past week, young Nigerians have ramped up widespread protests\xe2\x80\x94online and offline\xe2\x80\x94against rampant brutality by local police.\xf0\x9f\x93\xac Keep up with developments and emerging industries in Africa.Sign me upBy providing your email, you agree to the Quartz Privacy Policy.Feel the burnoutImage copyright: REUTERS/Adnan AbidiA tight schedule.When India entered a nationwide lockdown